{"id":123204,"type":6,"name":"西游记 (1999)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/bc/34/123204_54r4Q.jpg","rating":{"total":49,"count":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":2,"7":3,"8":25,"9":12,"10":5},"score":8.1},"summary":"　　经过九九八十一难，唐僧（徐少华 饰）师徒四人终于到达灵山，求取真经。修得正果，师徒一行驾云回到都城长安，见到唐王李世民（张志明 饰），并向其讲述了取景的经过。话说这一路真可谓艰难险阻，困难重重。通天河有灵感大王阻断行程，伤害性命；狮驼岭又有来自灵山的三神兽为妖作怪；期间更有师徒心生嫌隙，导致六耳猕猴趁虚而入，上演真假美猴王的好戏；更有金平府犀牛怪假冒佛祖，欺世盗名，引来天兵天将除妖。这万里艰辛，一言难尽……\r\n　　本片根据中国古典四大名著之一的《西游记》改编，当年囿于经费等原因，老版《西游记》并未全部拍完，《西游记续集》补全了缺失的部分。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>西游记续集</li><li><span>集数: </span>16</li><li><span>开始: </span>2000年</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>中国大陆</li><li><span>语言: </span>汉语普通话</li><li><span>每集长: </span>45分钟</li>","collection":{"collect":79,"doing":1,"on_hold":1,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"电视剧","count":11},{"name":"国产","count":11},{"name":"国产剧","count":8},{"name":"小说改","count":7},{"name":"中国","count":5},{"name":"四大名著","count":4},{"name":"大陆剧","count":2},{"name":"2000","count":2},{"name":"陆剧","count":1},{"name":"神作","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":468585,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/468585","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":468586,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/468586","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":468587,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/468587","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":468588,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/468588","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":468589,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/468589","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":468590,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/468590","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":468591,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/468591","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"",